---
---
<div class="panel varcard-panel">
  <div id="vcCorruptionGap" class="vc-corruption-gap" hidden role="status">
    <strong>恶堕进度缺失</strong>
    <span id="vcCorruptionGapMsg">已启用恶堕，但 MVU 尚无「恶堕进度」变量。可用「从卡推定变量」勾选补齐，或到状态栏重新生成。</span>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-ghost adult-btn-compact vc-gap-action" id="vcGapInferBtn">从卡推定补齐</button>
  </div>

  <div class="vc-node-workbench">
    <div class="vc-workbench-head">
      <div>
        <h2>MVU 变量节点</h2>
        <!-- 整套生成在状态栏；本页负责链路与变量查看/编辑 -->
        <p>节点编排与变量查看/编辑。整套变量请在「状态栏」生成并覆盖写入；也可
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-ghost adult-btn-compact" id="btnVcInfer">从卡推定变量</button>
          规则合并。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vc-workbench-meta">
        <span class="vc-mode-pill">手动链路模式</span>
        <span id="vcStatus" class="vc-status">自动同步角色卡中的 MVU…</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="vcInferPanel" class="vc-infer-panel" hidden>
      <div class="vc-infer-head">
        <strong>从卡推定 · 候选变量</strong>
        <span id="vcInferCount" class="vc-infer-count">0</span>
        <div class="vc-infer-head-actions">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" id="vcInferSelectAll">全选新增</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" id="vcInferSelectNone">全不选</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" id="vcInferCancel">关闭</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="vc-infer-tip">勾选后合并进 <code>zmer_mvu_design</code>（已有路径默认不勾）。不覆盖整套 AI 生成，仅 upsert。</p>
      <div id="vcInferList" class="vc-infer-list"></div>
      <div class="vc-infer-actions">
        <button type="button" class="btn" id="vcInferApply">应用合并</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="vcInferApplyInject">应用并注入</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="vc-node-canvas" id="vcNodeCanvas">
      <div class="vc-graph-toolbar">
        <button type="button" class="vc-graph-btn" id="vcZoomOut" title="缩小">−</button>
        <button type="button" class="vc-graph-btn" id="vcZoomReset" title="适应画布">适应</button>
        <button type="button" class="vc-graph-btn" id="vcZoomIn" title="放大">+</button>
        <button type="button" class="vc-graph-btn vc-graph-btn-arrange" id="vcGraphArrange" title="一键整理节点">整理</button>
        <button type="button" class="vc-graph-btn" id="vcGraphExpand" title="展开编辑">⛶</button>
        <span class="vc-graph-hint">拖节点移动，拖圆点连线，滚轮缩放</span>
      </div>

      <div class="vc-graph-viewport" id="vcGraphViewport">
        <div class="vc-graph-space" id="vcGraphSpace">
          <svg class="vc-node-lines" id="vcGraphSvg" viewBox="0 0 1900 980" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <g id="vcGraphWires"></g>
            <path class="vc-wire vc-wire-temp" id="vcTempWire" d="" />
          </svg>

      <section class="vc-node vc-flow-node vc-flow-input" data-node="user-message" style="left:48px; top:120px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-node-title">用户发消息</span>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-out" data-port="user-message:out" data-kind="out"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-node-desc">本轮输入进入 SillyTavern 生成流程。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="vc-node vc-flow-node vc-flow-st" data-node="st-prompt" style="left:310px; top:120px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-in" data-port="st-prompt:in" data-kind="in"></span>
          <span class="vc-node-title">SillyTavern 准备 Prompt</span>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-out" data-port="st-prompt:out" data-kind="out"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-node-desc">整理角色卡、聊天历史、预设、世界书和扩展注入。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="vc-node vc-flow-node vc-flow-worldbook" data-node="wb-constant" style="left:595px; top:48px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-in" data-port="wb-constant:in" data-kind="in"></span>
          <span class="vc-node-title">世界书常驻条目插入</span>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-out" data-port="wb-constant:out" data-kind="out"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-node-desc">例如变量更新规则、输出格式、强规则、运行法则。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="vc-node vc-flow-node vc-flow-variable" data-node="stat-data" style="left:595px; top:250px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-in" data-port="stat-data:in" data-kind="in"></span>
          <span class="vc-node-title">变量列表插入 stat_data</span>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-out" data-port="stat-data:out" data-kind="out"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-node-desc">通过变量列表条目把当前状态喂给模型。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="vc-node vc-flow-node vc-flow-ejs" data-node="ejs-router" style="left:895px; top:48px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-in" data-port="ejs-router:in" data-kind="in"></span>
          <span class="vc-node-title">EJS 控制器动态加载阶段世界书</span>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-out" data-port="ejs-router:out" data-kind="out"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-node-desc">按好感、阶段、标记决定哪些隐藏剧情条目参与本轮。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="vc-node vc-flow-node vc-flow-rule" data-node="rule-inject" style="left:895px; top:250px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-in" data-port="rule-inject:in" data-kind="in"></span>
          <span class="vc-node-title">Roll / 随机事件 / 阻尼器 / 交易规则注入</span>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-out" data-port="rule-inject:out" data-kind="out"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-node-desc">把好感 Roll、经济规则、随机事件和防暴走限制写进本轮提示。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="vc-node vc-flow-node vc-flow-model" data-node="model-generate" style="left:1215px; top:150px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-in" data-port="model-generate:in" data-kind="in"></span>
          <span class="vc-node-title">模型生成回复</span>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-out" data-port="model-generate:out" data-kind="out"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-node-desc">模型同时写剧情正文与变量更新块。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="vc-node vc-flow-node vc-flow-output" data-node="story-output" style="left:1510px; top:54px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-in" data-port="story-output:in" data-kind="in"></span>
          <span class="vc-node-title">输出 &lt;story&gt; 正文</span>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-out" data-port="story-output:out" data-kind="out"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-node-desc">展示给用户看的剧情文本。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="vc-node vc-flow-node vc-flow-update" data-node="update-output" style="left:1510px; top:250px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-in" data-port="update-output:in" data-kind="in"></span>
          <span class="vc-node-title">输出 &lt;UpdateVariable&gt;</span>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-out" data-port="update-output:out" data-kind="out"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-node-desc">模型在技术块里给出 JSONPatch 更新命令。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="vc-node vc-flow-node vc-flow-mvu" data-node="mvu-patch" style="left:1215px; top:470px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-in" data-port="mvu-patch:in" data-kind="in"></span>
          <span class="vc-node-title">MVU 解析 JSONPatch</span>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-out" data-port="mvu-patch:out" data-kind="out"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-node-desc">读取 replace / delta / insert / remove / move 等操作。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="vc-node vc-flow-node vc-flow-zod" data-node="zod-validate" style="left:895px; top:470px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-in" data-port="zod-validate:in" data-kind="in"></span>
          <span class="vc-node-title">Zod Schema 校验和自动处理</span>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-out" data-port="zod-validate:out" data-kind="out"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-node-desc">类型转换、默认值、范围限制、非法更新兜底。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="vc-node vc-node-varmap vc-flow-node vc-flow-variable" data-node="varmap" style="left:595px; top:470px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-in" data-port="varmap:in" data-kind="in"></span>
          <span class="vc-node-title">状态向量窗口</span>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-out" data-port="varmap:out" data-kind="out"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="vc-varmap-list" id="vcGraphVarMap">
          <div class="vc-varmap-empty">导入或生成 MVU 后，会在下方展开每个变量节点。</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="vc-node vc-flow-node vc-flow-event" data-node="status-event" style="left:310px; top:470px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-in" data-port="status-event:in" data-kind="in"></span>
          <span class="vc-node-title">VARIABLE_UPDATE_ENDED</span>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-out" data-port="status-event:out" data-kind="out"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-node-desc">状态栏收到变量更新结束事件后刷新显示。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="vc-node vc-flow-node vc-flow-regex" data-node="regex-display" style="left:48px; top:470px;">
        <div class="vc-node-head" data-drag-handle>
          <span class="vc-port vc-port-in" data-port="regex-display:in" data-kind="in"></span>
          <span class="vc-node-title">正则隐藏技术内容 / 美化正文和状态栏</span>
        </div>
        <p class="vc-node-desc">隐藏 UpdateVariable，仅显示剧情正文和美化后的状态变化。</p>
      </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ★ 生成结果 — 清单 + 可展开详情 -->
  <div id="vcResult" class="vc-result" style="display:none;">
    <div class="vc-checklist" id="vcChecklist"></div>

    <div class="vc-variable-preview" id="vcVariablePreview" style="display:none;">
      <div class="vc-preview-head">
        <strong>🧭 本次变量预览</strong>
        <span id="vcVariableCount">0 个状态向量</span>
      </div>
      <div class="vc-preview-sub">这些变量会写入角色卡，后续回复会按更新规则维护它们。</div>
      <div class="vc-single-tools">
        <input id="vcSingleRequirement" type="text" placeholder="单独追加变量，例如：埃利安的警惕值、店铺库存、隐藏线索..." />
        <button id="btnVcAddOne" type="button">＋ 生成一条</button>
      </div>
      <div class="vc-preview-grid" id="vcVariablePreviewList"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- 折叠详情 -->
    <details class="vc-details">
      <summary class="vc-details-toggle">📄 查看生成详情 / 逐项复制</summary>
      <div class="vc-details-body">
        <div class="vc-detail-block">
          <div class="vc-detail-head"><strong>📜 变量结构脚本</strong><span class="vc-badge script">酒馆助手脚本</span><button class="vc-copy-btn" data-target="vcCodeSchema">📋</button></div>
          <pre class="vc-pre"><code id="vcCodeSchema"></code></pre>
        </div>
        <div class="vc-detail-block">
          <div class="vc-detail-head"><strong>🎯 变量初始化</strong><span class="vc-badge wb-off">禁用条目</span><button class="vc-copy-btn" data-target="vcCodeInitvar">📋</button></div>
          <pre class="vc-pre"><code id="vcCodeInitvar"></code></pre>
        </div>
        <div class="vc-detail-block">
          <div class="vc-detail-head"><strong>🔄 更新规则</strong><span class="vc-badge wb-on">常驻条目</span><button class="vc-copy-btn" data-target="vcCodeUpdate">📋</button></div>
          <pre class="vc-pre"><code id="vcCodeUpdate"></code></pre>
        </div>
        <div class="vc-detail-block">
          <div class="vc-detail-head"><strong>📤 输出格式</strong><span class="vc-badge wb-on">D0 常驻</span><button class="vc-copy-btn" data-target="vcCodeFormat">📋</button></div>
          <pre class="vc-pre"><code id="vcCodeFormat"></code></pre>
        </div>
        <div class="vc-detail-block">
          <div class="vc-detail-head"><strong>📋 变量列表</strong><span class="vc-badge wb-on">D1 常驻</span><button class="vc-copy-btn" data-target="vcCodeVarlist">📋</button></div>
          <pre class="vc-pre"><code id="vcCodeVarlist"></code></pre>
        </div>
        <div class="vc-detail-block">
          <div class="vc-detail-head"><strong>🔧 正则脚本</strong><span class="vc-badge regex">自动注入</span><button class="vc-copy-btn" data-target="vcCodeRegex">📋</button></div>
          <pre class="vc-pre"><code id="vcCodeRegex"></code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- 底栏 -->
    <div class="vc-bottom">
      <span class="vc-summary" id="vcSummary"></span>
      <button id="btnVcClear" class="btn vc-clear-btn" type="button">🧹 清除变量</button>
      <button id="btnVcDelete" class="btn-icon btn-icon--danger vc-delete-btn" type="button" title="删除组件" aria-label="删除组件">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 7h16"/><path d="M9 7V5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v2"/><path d="M10 11v6M14 11v6"/><path d="M7 7l1 12a1 1 0 0 0 1 .9h6a1 1 0 0 0 1-.9l1-12"/></svg>
      </button>
      <button id="btnVcExport" class="btn vc-export-btn">💾 导出变量卡包</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ★★★ 样式 ★★★ -->
<style is:global>
  .varcard-panel {
    min-height: 760px;
    max-height: min(870px, calc(100vh - 112px));
    overflow-x: hidden;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .vc-node-workbench {
    position: relative;
    padding: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(51,65,85,0.9);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 18px 18px, rgba(148,163,184,0.14) 1px, transparent 1px) 0 0 / 24px 24px,
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15,23,42,0.96), rgba(2,6,23,0.92));
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  }

  .vc-workbench-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .vc-workbench-head h2 {
    margin: 0 0 4px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }
  .vc-workbench-head p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .vc-workbench-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 6px;
    max-width: min(320px, 42%);
  }
  .vc-mode-pill {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(52,211,153,0.28);
    background: rgba(6,78,59,0.28);
    color: #86efac;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .vc-workbench-meta .vc-status {
    display: block;
    min-height: 0;
    padding: 0;
    text-align: right;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    word-break: break-word;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .vc-corruption-gap {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.45);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(127, 29, 29, 0.55), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9));
    color: #fecaca;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .vc-corruption-gap[hidden] { display: none !important; }
  .vc-corruption-gap strong {
    color: #fee2e2;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin-right: 0.35em;
  }
  .vc-gap-action {
    display: inline-flex !important;
    width: auto !important;
    margin: 0 0 0 0.35em !important;
    vertical-align: baseline;
    color: #fde68a !important;
    border-color: rgba(253, 230, 138, 0.35) !important;
  }
  .vc-workbench-head p .adult-btn-compact,
  .vc-workbench-head p #btnVcInfer {
    display: inline-flex !important;
    width: auto !important;
    margin: 0 0.2em !important;
    vertical-align: baseline;
  }
  /* 与世界与限定行内按钮同款（本面板未挂 AdultConfig 样式时兜底） */
  .varcard-panel .adult-btn-compact {
    font-size: 0.7rem !important;
    padding: 2px 8px !important;
  }

  .vc-infer-panel {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.28);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.88);
  }
  .vc-infer-panel[hidden] { display: none !important; }
  .vc-infer-head {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .vc-infer-head strong {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
  }
  .vc-infer-count {
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
    color: #7dd3fc;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
  }
  .vc-infer-head-actions {
    margin-left: auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .vc-infer-tip {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .vc-infer-list {
    max-height: 240px;
    overflow: auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .vc-infer-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: start;
    padding: 6px 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.8);
    background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.55);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
  }
  .vc-infer-row.is-present { opacity: 0.72; }
  .vc-infer-row-main { min-width: 0; }
  .vc-infer-path {
    color: #e2e8f0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono, ui-monospace, monospace);
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  .vc-infer-meta {
    margin-top: 2px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.64rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .vc-infer-badge {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.35);
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .vc-infer-badge.is-new {
    border-color: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.4);
    color: #86efac;
  }
  .vc-infer-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .vc-node-canvas {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 380px;
  }
  .vc-graph-modal {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 14px;
    z-index: 2147483000;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.24);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 18px 18px, rgba(148,163,184,0.12) 1px, transparent 1px) 0 0 / 24px 24px,
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15,23,42,0.98), rgba(2,6,23,0.97));
    box-shadow: 0 28px 90px rgba(0,0,0,0.72);
  }
  .vc-graph-modal::before {
    content: "MVU 节点大屏编辑";
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    font-weight: 900;
  }
  .vc-graph-modal .vc-node-canvas {
    width: 100%;
    height: calc(100vh - 72px);
  }
  body.vc-graph-body-locked {
    overflow: hidden !important;
  }
  .vc-node-canvas.is-expanded {
    flex: 1 1 auto;
    min-height: 0;
  }

  .vc-graph-toolbar {
    position: absolute;
    right: 10px;
    top: 10px;
    z-index: 5;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 5px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(71,85,105,0.72);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(2,6,23,0.72);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }
  .vc-graph-btn {
    height: 26px;
    min-width: 28px;
    padding: 0 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.2);
    background: rgba(8,47,73,0.35);
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .vc-graph-btn:hover { background: rgba(14,116,144,0.42); }
  .vc-graph-btn-arrange {
    border-color: rgba(52,211,153,0.24);
    background: rgba(6,95,70,0.34);
    color: #bbf7d0;
  }
  .vc-graph-btn-arrange:hover {
    background: rgba(5,150,105,0.42);
    border-color: rgba(52,211,153,0.46);
  }
  .vc-graph-hint {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
    padding: 0 4px;
  }

  .vc-graph-viewport {
    position: relative;
    height: clamp(680px, 64vh, 820px);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(30,41,59,0.95);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(148,163,184,0.18) 1px, transparent 1px) 0 0 / 28px 28px,
      rgba(2,6,23,0.28);
    cursor: grab;
    touch-action: none;
  }
  .vc-node-canvas.is-expanded .vc-graph-viewport {
    height: 100%;
    min-height: 0;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }
  .vc-node-canvas.is-expanded .vc-graph-toolbar {
    top: 14px;
    right: 14px;
  }
  .vc-graph-viewport.is-panning { cursor: grabbing; }

  .vc-graph-space {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 1900px;
    height: 980px;
    transform-origin: 0 0;
    will-change: transform;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  .vc-node-lines {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    pointer-events: auto;
    z-index: 0;
    overflow: visible;
  }
  .vc-wire {
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 4;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 7px rgba(56,189,248,0.35));
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .vc-wire:hover { stroke-width: 6; }
  .vc-wire-hit {
    fill: none;
    stroke: rgba(255,255,255,0.001);
    stroke-width: 22;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    pointer-events: stroke;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .vc-wire-source { stroke: var(--color-accent-hover); }
  .vc-wire-require { stroke: var(--color-accent-hover); }
  .vc-wire-output { stroke: var(--color-success); }
  .vc-wire-var { stroke: var(--color-warning); stroke-width: 2.4; opacity: 0.88; }
  .vc-node-canvas.is-expanded .vc-wire-var {
    filter: none;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  .vc-wire-temp {
    stroke: var(--color-warning);
    stroke-dasharray: 10 8;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .vc-wire-temp.active { opacity: 1; }

  .vc-node {
    position: absolute;
    width: 280px;
    z-index: 1;
    border: 1px solid rgba(71,85,105,0.9);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(15,23,42,0.92);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.24), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    overflow: hidden;
    cursor: default;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .vc-node-source { width: 280px; }
  .vc-node-require { width: 300px; }
  .vc-node-engine { width: 260px; }
  .vc-node-output { width: 240px; }
  .vc-node-varmap { width: 318px; }
  .vc-node-varitem { width: 260px; }
  .vc-flow-node { width: 250px; }
  .vc-flow-st,
  .vc-flow-ejs,
  .vc-flow-rule,
  .vc-flow-zod,
  .vc-flow-regex { width: 286px; }
  .vc-flow-model,
  .vc-flow-update,
  .vc-flow-output,
  .vc-flow-mvu,
  .vc-flow-event { width: 250px; }
  .vc-flow-input .vc-node-head { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(20,83,45,0.94), rgba(15,23,42,0.84)); }
  .vc-flow-st .vc-node-head { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(14,116,144,0.8), rgba(15,23,42,0.84)); }
  .vc-flow-worldbook .vc-node-head { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(126,34,206,0.72), rgba(15,23,42,0.84)); }
  .vc-flow-variable .vc-node-head { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(6,95,70,0.78), rgba(15,23,42,0.84)); }
  .vc-flow-ejs .vc-node-head { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(180,83,9,0.7), rgba(15,23,42,0.84)); }
  .vc-flow-rule .vc-node-head { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(190,24,93,0.68), rgba(15,23,42,0.84)); }
  .vc-flow-model .vc-node-head { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(67,56,202,0.78), rgba(15,23,42,0.84)); }
  .vc-flow-output .vc-node-head { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(8,145,178,0.72), rgba(15,23,42,0.84)); }
  .vc-flow-update .vc-node-head { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(124,58,237,0.72), rgba(15,23,42,0.84)); }
  .vc-flow-mvu .vc-node-head { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(21,128,61,0.78), rgba(15,23,42,0.84)); }
  .vc-flow-zod .vc-node-head { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(13,148,136,0.7), rgba(15,23,42,0.84)); }
  .vc-flow-event .vc-node-head { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(202,138,4,0.68), rgba(15,23,42,0.84)); }
  .vc-flow-regex .vc-node-head { background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(219,39,119,0.62), rgba(15,23,42,0.84)); }

  .vc-node-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    min-height: 32px;
    padding: 7px 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(30,41,59,0.98), rgba(51,65,85,0.82));
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(71,85,105,0.75);
    cursor: move;
  }
  .vc-node-title {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.28;
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  }
  .vc-node-desc {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 10px 12px 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .vc-node-code-panel {
    padding: 8px 10px 10px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(71,85,105,0.4);
    background: rgba(2,6,23,0.18);
  }
  .vc-node-code-toggle {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    height: 22px;
    padding: 0 8px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.2);
    background: rgba(8,47,73,0.32);
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }
  .vc-node-code-toggle:hover {
    background: rgba(14,116,144,0.4);
    border-color: rgba(56,189,248,0.46);
  }
  .vc-node-code-body {
    display: none;
    margin-top: 7px;
  }
  .vc-node-code-panel.is-open .vc-node-code-body { display: block; }
  .vc-node-code-editor {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 84px;
    max-height: 260px;
    resize: vertical;
    padding: 7px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(71,85,105,0.74);
    background: rgba(2,6,23,0.72);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono','Fira Code','Consolas',monospace;
    font-size: 0.56rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .vc-node-code-hint {
    margin-top: 5px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.52rem;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }
  .vc-port {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.95);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(226,232,240,0.22), 0 0 10px currentColor;
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    background: currentColor;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    cursor: crosshair;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }
  .vc-port:hover { transform: scale(1.22); }
  .vc-port-in { color: var(--color-success); }
  .vc-node-engine .vc-port-in { color: var(--color-accent-hover); }
  .vc-node-engine .vc-port-out { color: var(--color-success); }
  .vc-node-require .vc-port-out { color: var(--color-accent-hover); }

  .vc-output-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 7px;
    padding: 12px;
  }
  .vc-output-list span {
    position: relative;
    padding: 7px 8px 7px 24px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.16);
    background: rgba(8,47,73,0.22);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
  }
  .vc-output-list span::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 9px;
    top: 50%;
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    background: var(--color-success);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(52,211,153,0.5);
  }

  .vc-varmap-list {
    max-height: 92px;
    overflow: auto;
    padding: 8px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 6px;
    background: rgba(2,6,23,0.18);
  }
  .vc-varmap-empty {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
    padding: 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(100,116,139,0.28);
  }
  .vc-varnode-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 4px;
    padding: 7px;
    background: rgba(2,6,23,0.2);
  }
  .vc-varmap-item {
    display: grid;
    gap: 4px;
    padding: 7px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(34,211,238,0.14);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(8,47,73,0.32), rgba(15,23,42,0.52));
  }
  .vc-varmap-path {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.64rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  .vc-varmap-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .vc-varmap-desc {
    margin-top: 6px;
    color: #dbeafe;
    font-size: 0.64rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
    word-break: break-word;
  }
  .vc-varmap-check {
    margin-top: 5px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
    word-break: break-word;
  }
  .vc-varmap-chip {
    max-width: 100%;
    padding: 2px 5px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    background: rgba(15,23,42,0.7);
    border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.12);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono','Fira Code','Consolas',monospace;
    font-size: 0.52rem;
    line-height: 1.35;
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  .vc-varmap-chip.update {
    color: var(--color-success);
    border-color: rgba(52,211,153,0.18);
  }

  /* ── 结果 ── */
  .vc-result { animation: vcFade 0.35s ease; }
  @keyframes vcFade { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(12px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }

  /* ── 清单 ── */
  .vc-checklist { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .vc-check-item {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px;
    padding: 7px 10px; border-radius: 6px;
    background: rgba(15,23,42,0.5); border: 1px solid var(--color-surface);
    font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .vc-check-item.ok { border-color: rgba(52,211,153,0.3); }
  .vc-check-icon { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .vc-check-label { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .vc-check-badge {
    font-size: 0.56rem; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 99px;
    background: rgba(139,92,246,0.1); color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.2);
  }

  .vc-variable-preview {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.18);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(8,47,73,0.26), rgba(15,23,42,0.55)),
      rgba(2,6,23,0.38);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .vc-preview-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.12);
    background: rgba(15,23,42,0.56);
  }
  .vc-preview-head strong {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
  }
  .vc-preview-head span {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: #67e8f9;
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }
  .vc-preview-sub {
    padding: 8px 12px 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .vc-single-tools {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 12px 0;
  }
  .vc-single-tools input {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(71,85,105,0.9);
    background: rgba(2,6,23,0.52);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    padding: 0 10px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
  }
  .vc-single-tools button,
  .vc-var-action {
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.24);
    background: rgba(8,47,73,0.34);
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-weight: 700;
    transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .vc-single-tools button {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    height: 32px;
    padding: 0 10px;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
  }
  .vc-single-tools button:hover,
  .vc-var-action:hover {
    background: rgba(14,116,144,0.42);
    border-color: rgba(56,189,248,0.48);
  }
  .vc-preview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 12px 12px;
    max-height: 330px;
    overflow: auto;
  }
  .vc-var-group {
    border: 1px solid rgba(71,85,105,0.72);
    border-radius: 7px;
    background: rgba(15,23,42,0.72);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .vc-var-group-title {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 7px 9px;
    color: #f8fafc;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: rgba(51,65,85,0.62);
  }
  .vc-var-group-title span {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }
  .vc-var-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 8px;
  }
  .vc-var-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    gap: 4px 8px;
    padding: 7px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: rgba(2,6,23,0.44);
    border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.1);
  }
  .vc-var-path {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  .vc-var-type {
    align-self: start;
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(52,211,153,0.2);
    color: #86efac;
    background: rgba(6,78,59,0.16);
    font-size: 0.54rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }
  .vc-var-desc,
  .vc-var-default {
    grid-column: 1;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
    word-break: break-word;
  }
  .vc-var-default code {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono','Fira Code','Consolas',monospace;
  }
  .vc-var-actions {
    grid-column: 2;
    grid-row: 2 / span 2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: stretch;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .vc-var-action {
    padding: 2px 6px;
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .vc-var-action.danger {
    border-color: rgba(248,113,113,0.28);
    background: rgba(127,29,29,0.22);
    color: var(--color-danger);
  }
  .vc-var-action.danger:hover {
    border-color: rgba(248,113,113,0.52);
    background: rgba(127,29,29,0.38);
  }

  /* ── 折叠详情 ── */
  .vc-details { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .vc-details-toggle {
    font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--color-accent); cursor: pointer;
    padding: 6px 0; list-style: none; font-weight: 600; transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .vc-details-toggle:hover { color: var(--color-accent-hover); }
  .vc-details-toggle::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .vc-details[open] .vc-details-toggle { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .vc-details-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }

  .vc-detail-block {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-surface); border-radius: 6px;
    background: rgba(2,6,23,0.4); overflow: hidden;
  }
  .vc-detail-head {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 8px 10px; background: rgba(15,23,42,0.6);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-surface); flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .vc-detail-head strong { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); }
  .vc-badge {
    font-size: 0.54rem; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 99px; font-weight: 700; display: inline-block;
  }
  .vc-badge.script { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.12); color: var(--color-warning); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.25); }
  .vc-badge.wb-off { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1);   color: var(--color-danger); border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.2); }
  .vc-badge.wb-on  { background: rgba(56,189,248,0.1);  color: var(--color-accent-hover);  border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.2); }
  .vc-badge.regex  { background: rgba(244,114,182,0.1); color: #f9a8d4; border: 1px solid rgba(244,114,182,0.2); }

  .vc-copy-btn {
    margin-left: auto; font-size: 0.66rem; padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.2);
    background: var(--color-accent-soft); color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; font-family: inherit;
  }
  .vc-copy-btn:hover { background: rgba(139,92,246,0.18); border-color: rgba(139,92,246,0.4); }

  .vc-pre {
    margin: 0; padding: 10px; overflow-x: auto;
    font-size: 0.68rem; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-height: 260px; scrollbar-width: thin;
  }
  .vc-pre code { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono','Fira Code','Consolas',monospace; white-space: pre; }

  /* ── 底栏 ── */
  .vc-bottom {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-surface); flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .vc-summary { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); flex: 1; min-width: 0; line-height: 1.5; word-break: break-word; }
  .vc-export-btn {
    background: rgba(56,189,248,0.08) !important; color: var(--color-accent-hover) !important;
    border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,0.2) !important;
    font-weight: 600; padding: 7px 14px !important; font-size: 0.72rem !important;
    border-radius: 7px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .vc-export-btn:hover { background: rgba(56,189,248,0.18) !important; border-color: rgba(56,189,248,0.45) !important; }
  .vc-clear-btn {
    background: rgba(239,68,68,0.08) !important; color: var(--color-danger) !important;
    border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.22) !important;
    font-weight: 600; padding: 7px 14px !important; font-size: 0.72rem !important;
